Class ChannelInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.usgs.volcanoes.swarm.ChannelUtil
      • gov.usgs.volcanoes.swarm.AbstractChannelInfo
        • gov.usgs.volcanoes.swarm.ChannelInfo
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IChannelInfo
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ChannelGroupInfo

    public class ChannelInfo
extends AbstractChannelInfo
    Base channel information without groups. This class should be extended and the 'getGroups()' method should be over-ridden if group support is desired.
    Author:
    Kevin Frechette (ISTI)
